                        <div class="description">
                            <h4 class="hed"><a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/texas-border-wall-contracts-land-trump-administration">The Trump Administration Keeps Awarding Border Wall Contracts but Doesn’t Own the Land to Build On</a></h4>
                                                    <p class="dek">The government’s strategy of awarding contracts before acquiring titles to land in Texas has led to millions of dollars in costs for delays. Things could get even more complicated if President-elect Joe Biden stops border wall construction.</p>
                                                </div>
                    </div>

    
                            
                    <div class="story-entry section-articles">

                        
