                            <h4 class="hed"><a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/trumps-immigration-pick-attacked-obama-programs-in-ghost-written-senate">Trump’s Immigration Pick Attacked Obama Programs in Ghost-Written Senate Letters</a></h4>
                                                    <p class="dek">If letters written by Lee Francis Cissna, the president’s nominee to head U.S. Citizenship and Immigration Services, are any guide, he’s poised to dismantle Obama-era policies like a humanitarian program for Central American children.</p>
